o, (b) the height of $\\mu$ is $m$, (c) the height of $\\lambda$ is $\\le\nm^\\epsilon$, and (d) $|\\lambda|=|\\mu| \\le m^3$. The proof of the last result\nillustrates the effectiveness of the explicit proof strategy of GCT.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Jul 2015 16:19:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 21 Jul 2017 17:32:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-02"}
